    "name": "幽林深处 Heart of the Forest",
    "steam_appid": 3274320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一场穿越黑森林的不幸徒步途中，一群性格迥异的学生被困于密林深处的复仇怨灵缠上。如今，他们必须一边挣扎求生，一边竭力挣脱怨灵的腐化侵蚀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恐惧、创伤与过往的秘密如影随形，每位角色都被逼至崩溃的边缘。在德国独立工作室 <i>Trapped Predator</i> 打造的这款互动式心理恐怖游戏中，他们的生死存亡全由你的选择决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着剧情逐步展开，队员们将直面内心最深处的恐惧与过往阴霾。谁能幸存？在这场穿越密林的恐怖旅程中，帮助主角们死里逃生吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/2d9b823159cbb7f93cedfa187ee10a8a.poster.avif?t=1771856142\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/2d9b823159cbb7f93cedfa187ee10a8a.webm?t=1771856142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/2d9b823159cbb7f93cedfa187ee10a8a.mp4?t=1771856142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >黑森林的惊魂之旅</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于源自德国民间传说的惊悚叙事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入角色们的不幸徒步，深入神秘而壮美的黑森林，探索这片孕育了无数神话传说的秘境。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/b80559941eb22b01a0b904c30d1dc867.poster.avif?t=1771856142\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/b80559941eb22b01a0b904c30d1dc867.webm?t=1771856142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/b80559941eb22b01a0b904c30d1dc867.mp4?t=1771856142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的抉择关乎生死</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谁能幸存？在这场穿越密林的恐怖旅程中，帮助主角们死里逃生吧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心腐化的侵蚀，否则你将沦为潜伏于森林深处的黑暗力量的猎物。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/02b5821587c1bc4b79af751ce0a65ee8.poster.avif?t=1771856142\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/02b5821587c1bc4b79af751ce0a65ee8.webm?t=1771856142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/02b5821587c1bc4b79af751ce0a65ee8.mp4?t=1771856142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多视角叙事</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随多位角色的故事线，游戏过程中视角将不断切换，让你透过他们的双眼，亲手塑造剧情走向。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/bbfe39e2a104a4237b2fa0cd8c39e87e.poster.avif?t=1771856142\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/bbfe39e2a104a4237b2fa0cd8c39e87e.webm?t=1771856142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274320/extras/bbfe39e2a104a4237b2fa0cd8c39e87e.mp4?t=1771856142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
